thread.title: BRIEF-Nic Posts Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.16

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nic Posts Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.16
text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Nic Inc:
* NIC EARNS 16 CENTS PER SHARE IN FOURTH QUARTER 2017 ON TOTAL REVENUES OF $83.5 MILLION; EXCEEDS HIGH END OF ANNUAL GUIDANCE
* Q4 REVENUE $83.5 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $81 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.16 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.16 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* ‍Q4 2017 PORTAL REVENUES WERE $78.4 MILLION, A 7 PERCENT INCREASE OVER Q4 OF 2016​
* QTRLY TOTAL REVENUES $83.5 MILLION VERSUS $78.3 MLN‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
